Description: Plain-text file markdown note taking with Nextcloud/ownCloud integration
 Plain-text file markdown note taking with Nextcloud/ownCloud integration.
 You own your own notes! All notes are stored as plain-text files on your desktop computer.
 Sync them over devices (desktop & mobile) with ownCloud.
 Use Nextcloud Notes to edit your notes in the web.
